narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Breadth of detailed, useful info about this critical period of Russian history.
This course deepened my knowledge of Russian history, especially the history of Russia before the Bolshevik revolution.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The material we read each class was very informative and the class discussions helped deepen my understanding of the material.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: This class is really fun, and you'll learn a lot. Just be prepared to do a substantial amount of reading.
I would recommend this course for anyone looking to further deepen their knowledge of Russian history. There is a fair amount of reading but all of it is very relevant and interesting.
